item.title: Trifecta
item.description: So I’ve been on a personal growth journey on something you’ll least expect me to pursue: posing. As out of character as it sounds I promise there’s a deeper meaning somewhere; please bear with me. This journey was triggered when my mission to keep running fun (a story for another day) was met by the observation that all my trail photos look the same; different backgrounds but airplane arms all over the place.
